'''Cebu City Sharks''' also known as '''Cebu City Sharks-Casino Ethyl Alcohol''' is a professional basketball team in the [[Maharlika Pilipinas Basketball League]] (MPBL). The team is owned by the local government of [[Cebu|Cebu City]] and '''International Pharmaceuticals Incorporated''' with sponsorship from '''Casino Ethyl Alcohol'''.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.spin.ph/basketball/news/cebu-city-sharks-excited-over-chance-to-play-more-home-games-in-mbpl-debut|title=Cebu City Sharks excited over chance to play more home games in MPBL debut|last=Panerio|first=Jonas|date=May 22, 2018|work=Spin.ph|access-date=May 23, 2018}}</ref>

