'''Estadio Luis Alfonso Giagni''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Villa Elisa, Paraguay|Villa Elisa]], [[Paraguay]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Club Sol de América]].  The stadium holds 5,000 people. 

