{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Estadio Universitario UES | photo = | nickname = | image = [[Image:Estadio Universitario (UES).JPG|250px]]||
fullname = Estadio Universitario "Héroes y Mártires del 30 de Julio de 1975".| location = [[San Salvador]], [[El Salvador]] | built = 28 February 2003 [http://www.elsalvador.com/noticias/2003/03/01/deportes/depor7.shtml Inauguran complejo en la UES]| renovated = | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | surface = Grass | construction_cost = $30,000 thousand [[United States dollar|USD]] | architect = | former_names = | tenants = [[C.D. Universidad de El Salvador|C.D. UES]] (2003–) | seating_capacity = 10,000| }}
'''Estadio Universitario UES''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[San Salvador]], [[El Salvador]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[C.D. Universidad de El Salvador|C.D. UES]]. The stadium holds 10,000 people.<ref>http://www.laprensagrafica.com/2016/03/01/el-ues-de-nuevo-en-casa</ref>
