{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2018}} {{Use Indian English|date=July 2018}} {{Infobox sports team | team = Kolkata Vipers | current = | color1 = | color2 = | logo = | pixels = | founded = 2011 | league = [[Elite Football League of India|EFLI]] | history = | arena = | ballpark = | stadium = Vipers Stadium, 1,000 capacity | city = [[Kolkata]], [[West Bengal]], [[India]] | colors = Purple, Gold, Dark Green, White {{color box|#3b0160}} {{color box|#f0bf00}} {{color box|#003614}} {{color box|#FFFFFF}} | colours = | owner = | president = | coach = TBD | manager = | championships = | titles = | cheerleaders = | dancers = | mascot = | broadcasters = | media = | website = | uniforms = }}
The '''Kolkata Vipers''' are a professional [[American football]] team based in [[Kolkata]], [[India]]. The Vipers are one of the first eight franchises of the [[Elite Football League of India]] (EFLI) and compete in its inaugural season in [[2012 Elite Football League of India season|2012]] as a member of the East Division.<ref>{{cite web|title=EFLI - Match Schedule|url=http://www.efli.com/match-schedule.php|work=EFLI.com|publisher=EFLI|accessdate=21 December 2011}}</ref>
