{{Infobox handball club| | image = | fullname = Sporto mokykla Tauras-Vilnius kolegija Vilnius | shortname = SM Tauras-Vilniaus kolegija | founded = | ground = [[Tauras Handball Hall]] | capacity = | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Lithuanian Women's Handball League|LWHL]] | season = | position = | website = | colour1 = Blue | colour2 = Black | pattern_la1 = | pattern_b1 = | pattern_ra1 = | leftarm1 = | body1 = | rightarm1 = | shorts1 = }} '''SM Tauras-Vilniaus kolegija''' (formerly '''Eastcon AG Vilnius'''<ref>[http://www.delfi.lt/sportas/kitos-sporto-sakos/lietuvos-moteru-rankinio-cempionato-finalo-serijas-favorites-pradejo-pergalingai.d?id=61363197 Lietuvos moterų rankinio čempionato finalo serijas favoritės pradėjo pergalingai]</ref>) is a women's [[team handball]] club from [[Vilnius]], [[Lithuania]]. Currently club is competing in Lithuanian Handball League.
